name: The Teeniest Oller - bigsmol of "Hacienda La Fortuna" by Francisco Oller - by Lorem Ipsum
description: The upscaled version of a base 20 x 10 teeny "replica" of the painting "Hacienda La Fortuna" (1885) by the Puerto Rican Impressionist Francisco Oller. It depicts the aforementioned plantation during a workday.
